metadata.description: Mysterious space beings, searching the galaxy for their source of power. Along the way, they train their minds and bodies to level up, battle each other for supremacy, and call upon other Humach for support. Humach posses the ancient knowledge required to activate Genesis Machinie and generate $floppy. They can use $floppy to discover the truth about their mysterious origins, as well as to call in additional Humach (breed). Call transmission cost is lower the more Humach level up.
metadata.name: Humach #2238
